hyperpipe_info.flowchart:
Layout:
[StandardScaler][PCA][ImbalancedDataTransformer][estimators][SVC]
Relate:
[StandardScaler]->[PCA]
[PCA]->[ImbalancedDataTransformer]
[ImbalancedDataTransformer]->[estimators]
[estimators]->[SVC]

[StandardScaler]:
Define:
default
[PCA]:
Define:
n_components: FloatRange(start: 0.5,
                                   stop: 0.8, 
                                   step: 0.1, 
                                   range_type: range)
disabled: [False, True]
[ImbalancedDataTransformer]:
Define:
method_name: ['RandomUnderSampler', 'SMOTE']
disabled: [False, True]
[estimators]:
Layout:
[DecisionTreeClassifier]|
[LinearSVC]|


[estimators.DecisionTreeClassifier]:
Define:
min_samples_split: IntegerRange(start: 2,
                                   stop: 4, 
                                   step: None, 
                                   range_type: range)
criterion: gini

[estimators.LinearSVC]:
Define:
C: FloatRange(start: 0.5,
                                   stop: 25, 
                                   step: None, 
                                   range_type: range)
[SVC]:

kernel: rbf
